        .top__fulima__main__center__icon2
          = image_tag "icon-03.png", class: "image100" , height: "340px" , width: "220px"
        .top__fulima__main__center__title2
          売上金は即日振込みに対応
        .top__fulima__main__left__text2
          午前9時までに振込を依頼いただけれ
        .dr
